<collectingCountry box="[773,837,1606,1630]" name="China" pageId="11" pageNumber="596">China</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="LIAN, Y." box="[858,979,1606,1630]" pageId="11" pageNumber="596" pagination="30 - 33" refId="ref43135" refString="LIAN, Y. 2009. Description of a large armoured spider newly recorded genus: Perania Thorell, 1890 (Araneae: Tetrablemmidae) from Yunnan, China. Life Science Research 13 (1): 30 - 33." type="journal article" year="2009">Lian, 2009</bibRefCitation>
; Fig. 1, localities 1-3). It most likely also occurs in Burmese territory between these localities. FIG. 2
</paragraph>
